></blockquote><br />\n除左AML d contract 工之外<br />\n一出黎最搵錢一定係做frontline sales 升又升得最快 但壓力就最大 要孭數<br />\nretail姐係對一般大眾個人客戶 commercial 對工商客 一般無經驗無可能入到commercial 世界"},{"pid":"9feb239567772272b11009b38bc9e7201288651e","tid":471019,"uid":95180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想了解多d呢行 通常freshgrad 入邊d dep會比較有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問之前有google過下 但好少有好update好detail既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到有retail, commercial, wealth management呢d 想知其實有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左AML d contract 工之外<br />\n一出黎最搵錢一定係做frontline sales 升又升得最快 但壓力就最大 要孭數<br />\nretail姐係對一般大眾個人客戶 commercial 對工商客 一般無經驗無可能入到commercial 世界</blockquote><br />\nretail 同commercial 對客 即係其實都係要跑數? 其實成日聽人講banker banker 其實係咪全部都係跑數sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打 我好多野都想知 希望唔好覺得我煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18822ff9b245d1c50f65e686830ff1a638dd8b3e","tid":471019,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎 但係而加有外資bank比offer 1516緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資做左幾耐？做緊咩department？會轉去咩department? 中資係boc?</blockquote><br />\nboc做左一年 做緊frontline retail<br />\n而加大貓比左offer 轉做business banking 都係frontline<br />\n做唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽人講日日9-10先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走啦<br />\nBOC真係不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: BOC過3年幾<br />\n想等臨退休先返去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a51d3300ba89ea246d8ade47f387ae2213d9e56","tid":471019,"uid":25751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"做緊澳門本地銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb8740172ddcfca8e7cd2dd209ebeb3b7856107","tid":471019,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:48:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"30edc1f00b58261f80bee9a1d5b6d22351870376","tid":471019,"uid":55298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎 但係而加有外資bank比offer 1516緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資做左幾耐？做緊咩department？會轉去咩department? 中資係boc?</blockquote><br />\nboc做左一年 做緊frontline retail<br />\n而加大貓比左offer 轉做business banking 都係frontline<br />\n做唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽人講日日9-10先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCMB AM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做commercial/ corporate banking 老真講未必有做retail sales搵咁多，但壓力輕好多，sales味無咁濃，反而係做好多paper work既野，例如credit proposal/ account operation 之類，湊客成份多D"},{"pid":"aa5d62ad3fdf1381939117442f6decc2b9817d53","tid":471019,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"做緊teller狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b1b9ff43f830ccaf0cf263e9c76b785c068723","tid":471019,"uid":107184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎 但係而加有外資bank比offer 1516緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資做左幾耐？做緊咩department？會轉去咩department? 中資係boc?</blockquote><br />\nboc做左一年 做緊frontline retail<br />\n而加大貓比左offer 轉做business banking 都係frontline<br />\n做唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽人講日日9-10先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCMB AM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做commercial/ corporate banking 老真講未必有做retail sales搵咁多，但壓力輕好多，sales味無咁濃，反而係做好多paper work既野，例如credit proposal/ account operation 之類，湊客成份多D</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係做commercial 好過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890521bf01efe81a86b4c8338678eb7200fdd48b","tid":471019,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"corporate loan留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f31230791e862fda8c4a79264b789ba3492838","tid":471019,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎 但係而加有外資bank比offer 1516緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資做左幾耐？做緊咩department？會轉去咩department? 中資係boc?</blockquote><br />\nboc做左一年 做緊frontline retail<br />\n而加大貓比左offer 轉做business banking 都係frontline<br />\n做唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽人講日日9-10先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCMB AM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做commercial/ corporate banking 老真講未必有做retail sales搵咁多，但壓力輕好多，sales味無咁濃，反而係做好多paper work既野，例如credit proposal/ account operation 之類，湊客成份多D</blockquote><br />\ncorporate rm上年收十個月bonus<br />\nfrontline srm燈尾都追到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3444a07658eff21e5030f63af81f7c96d2b530ab","tid":471019,"uid":107184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"咁多位 但我而加大貓offer俾我個位話就話frontline 但係non sales role黎 邊個career path好d"},{"pid":"8e02eb0fc7e938bc9b4a01390dd037dac063c22d","tid":471019,"uid":55298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎 但係而加有外資bank比offer 1516緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資做左幾耐？做緊咩department？會轉去咩department? 中資係boc?</blockquote><br />\nboc做左一年 做緊frontline retail<br />\n而加大貓比左offer 轉做business banking 都係frontline<br />\n做唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽人講日日9-10先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCMB AM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做commercial/ corporate banking 老真講未必有做retail sales搵咁多，但壓力輕好多，sales味無咁濃，反而係做好多paper work既野，例如credit proposal/ account operation 之類，湊客成份多D</blockquote><br />\ncorporate rm上年收十個月bonus<br />\nfrontline srm燈尾都追到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊間十個月bonus咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以我所知一般Corp RM bonus都係3-6個月，出到十個應該係腦細關照，appraisal 好好<br />\n<br />\nRetail 既RM 人工個老底唔會差corp RM好多，幾乎差唔多，有quarterly bonus/ annual bonus，特別係果d premier banking果類既RM 搵好撚多架，當然跑數壓力好撚大，日日捽，表現唔好重開大會鞭<br />\n<br />\n做corp就好少會話點捽，更睇重係湊客既能力，始終公司用邊間銀行既服務都係睇返產品同效率，同個RM關係係咪好好係次要"},{"pid":"994aa916e6f2627d8cd4f4a4bedafe5f450f5d62","tid":471019,"uid":55298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做緊中資行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係喎 但係而加有外資bank比offer 1516緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資做左幾耐？做緊咩department？會轉去咩department? 中資係boc?</blockquote><br />\nboc做左一年 做緊frontline retail<br />\n而加大貓比左offer 轉做business banking 都係frontline<br />\n做唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  聽人講日日9-10先收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCMB AM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做commercial/ corporate banking 老真講未必有做retail sales搵咁多，但壓力輕好多，sales味無咁濃，反而係做好多paper work既野，例如credit proposal/ account operation 之類，湊客成份多D</blockquote><br />\n咁姐係做commercial 好過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇性格啦清<br />\n<br />\n鍾意面對面對客定湊公司客，完全係sales，所謂公司客你面對既人即係公司做financing既人，佢地都係打工，sale味無乜"},{"pid":"faf4f0a6f58928d1e627b0840a68bd46aaab8c56","tid":471019,"uid":8767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"以前外資retail rm<br />\n而家外資commercial bank RM , 跑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都呼籲想做bank 嘅手足唔好做retail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cba947e97fea5362112276a4fe596712241f923","tid":471019,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前外資retail rm<br />\n而家外資commercial bank RM , 跑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都呼籲想做bank 嘅手足唔好做retail<img src=\"/assets/f